name: SDO_Sequence.getProperty
purpose: Return the property for the specified sequence index.

return.description: An SDO_Model_Property. A return value of NULL means the sequence element does not belong to a property and must therefore be unstructured text.

errors:
SDO_IndexOutOfBoundsException
     
     
      
       Thrown if the sequence index is less than
       zero or greater than the size of the sequence.
